@{
    Layout = "/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}
<h1>What is new in vNext</h1>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Open Source</strong> - runs on Windows, Mac and Linux <sup>*</sup></li>
    <li><strong>Built in Memory</strong> - does not write files to disk, just need to refresh the browser to recompile</li>
    <li><strong>No System.Web dependency</strong></li>
    <li><strong>New Project System</strong> - based on the project.json and NuGet</li>
    <li><strong>Dependency Injection</strong> - in alpha is limited to constructor injection</li>
</ul>

<small>* Still in alpha and somethings require extra work current to get running on Linux or the Mac</small>

